Responsibilities 
We need experienced applied data scientists to empower the rest of Microsoftâ€™s teams and customers to build on the Core Search and AI teamâ€™s industrial grade machine learning. For example, we are investing deeply in enterprise search through Azure Cognitive Searchâ€™s recent semantic search launch. A critical part of the role is to develop an end-to-end understanding of Core Search and AI models and to adapt these models and techniques to new search challenges across the company. This role will require solving both data science and engineering challenges. 
Fine-tune, domain adapt and distill large scale NLP models for real-world large-scale applications. 
Develop an intuition for strategies to use across diverse, multi-lingual customer datasets and challenges. 
Adapt unstructured domain agnostic models and techniques to be robust when processing structured and semi-structured data. 
